🍽️ Restaurant Order Page
This project is a web-based interface for placing restaurant orders. Users can browse the menu, add items to their cart, and submit orders.

🚀 Features
View full restaurant menu with item descriptions

order now items from cart


🛠️ Tech Stack
Frontend: HTML, CSS, JavaScript (React optional)

Backend: Node.js / Express (if applicable)

Styling: CSS / Bootstrap / Tailwind (based on your setup)

📦 Installation
Clone the repo
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/restaurant-order-page.git

Navigate to the project folder
cd restaurant-order-page

Install dependencies
npm install

Start the server
npm start

📄 Usage
Open your browser and go to http://localhost:3000 to start ordering!






